    culturalInsight: 'Chinese astrology emphasizes cyclical time and collective patterns. The 60-year cycle (Sexagenary Cycle) mirrors FRC\'s recognition that patterns repeat and evolve across longer timeframes. Where Chinese astrology excels in understanding collective and generational patterns, FRC adds precision in daily timing.',
