    ],
    practicalBridge: [
      'Your Mayan day sign indicates your primary Phase configuration',
      'The tone number (1-13) suggests dimensional intensity levels',
      'Portal days correlate with high Field dimension sensitivity',
      'Galactic cycles align with longer-term FRC pattern shifts',
      'The uinal (20-day period) creates a mini-cycle of dimensional emphasis',
    ],
    culturalInsight: 'Mayan timekeeping was deeply integrated with ceremony and cosmic awareness. The calendar wasn\'t just for tracking days—it was a spiritual technology for alignment. FRC shares this vision of time as meaningful pattern, not mere measurement.',
